text: Patriarch Antony I or Patriarch Anthony I may refer to: * Antony I of Constantinople, Archbishop of Constantinople and Ecumenical Patriarch from 821 to 837 * Antony I, Serbian Patriarch, Archbishop of Peć and Serbian Patriarch from 1571 to 1574 * Antony I, Eritrean Patriarch, Archbishop of Asmara and Eritrean Patriarch from 2004 to 2007 ==See also== * Patriarch (disambiguation) * Antony (disambiguation)
title: Patriarch Antony I
